data.description: THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME HAS BEEN UPGRADED AND BACK ON THE MARKET.  Located on the LAKE and inside the sought after, gated community of Lake St. Clair. This quaint community has NO CDD. The home offers an open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, office/den and a 3-car garage with rear entrance to huge, fenced backyard. Entering the foyer, you will notice the inviting feel of this home. To the left is a den/office and to the right is a formal dining room. The gourmet kitchen overlooks the great room with vaulted ceilings and ample space for entertaining. The large master bedroom has a cozy ambience. The bathroom en suite has dual sinks and a large shower and walk-in closet. Secondary bedrooms are spacious and share a full bath. Exit from the great room through the sliding glass door into a fully enclosed Florida room. This ADDITIONAL 240 sqft (not included in living space measurements) provides a hybrid feature between comfort of indoor while enjoying the outdoors and the stunning view of Lake St Clair. Enjoy the SPECTACULAR sunsets from your private dock on the lake. Nice size stand-alone shed provides extra storage for your fishing poles. This amazing private gated community has lovely homes that surround their private “no wake” lake where you can enjoy fishing, canoeing, kayaking and even a low powered pontoon boat. Call Today for a private showing as this is a rare find!
